察法》《中华人民共和国公职人员政务处分法》等有关规定，经中央纪委常委会会议研究并报中共中央批准，决定给予杜兆才开除党籍处分；由国家监委给予其开除公职处分；收缴其违纪违法所得；将其涉嫌犯罪问题移送检察机关依法审查起诉，所涉财物一并移送。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-a03bba7c77ca3d705768b0c5d5d4408a_1440w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "23 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/624980075"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIwI6m4sy8x8NREAMaCTEwMTE2MzYzNyDDiISpBjAAOPMFQDByCTYyNDk4MDA3NXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "49_1696741348.482790", "card_id": "Q_624976283", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 22}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "火箭弹袭击已造成 1 死 16 人伤，以色列国防军宣布进入战争状态，哪些信息值得关注？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "本文转自【 CCTV 国际时讯】； 更新：根据以色列急救组织最新消息，火箭弹袭击已造成以色列 1 人死亡、 16 人受伤，其中 2 人伤势严重。目前，以色列国防军宣布进入战争状态。与此同时，耶路撒冷拉响防空警报。（总台记者 赵兵） 火箭弹袭击已造成 1 死 16 人伤，以色列国防军宣布进入战争状态 _ 急救 _ 赵兵 _ 组织"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "22 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/624976283"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IwI6m4sy8x8NREAMaCTEwMTE2MjgxMiCl8oOpBjAAODJAMXIJNjI0OTc2MjgzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}], "paging": {"is_end": true, "is_start": false, "next": "", "previous": "", "totals": 0}, "fresh_text": "热榜已更新", "display_num": 15, "display_first": true, "fb_bill_main_rise": 0, "head_zone": {"type": "billboard_lantern", "data": [{"id": "1683447529524715520", "link_url": "https://www.zhihu.com/org/pi-yao-qian-xian", "title": "辟谣专区", "source_type": 0, "attached_info": "Ci4QABoTMTY4MzQ0NzUyOTUyNDcxNTUyMHITMTY4MzQ0NzUyOTUyNDcxNTUyMHgA", "tag": "辟谣", "tag_bg_color": "GRD01A"}]}}